No. 921,

Misc.

Wilson v. Schnettler et al. Gerald W. Getty for petitioner. Solicitor General Rankin, Assistant Attorney General Wilkey, *841Beatrice Rosenberg and Kirby W. Patterson for the United States in opposition.

*840Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Seventh Circuit granted. Case transferred to the appellate docket.
